fulltitle: Cecil McBee discusses bebop and his contribution to post-bop
description: Cecil McBee is a featured artist for the Learning from Performers program of the Office for the Arts at Harvard, November 4-6, 2010.
title: Cecil McBee discusses bebop and his contribution to post-bop
